Title: Google Analytics Map Control
Description: Display Google Analytics Map in ASP.NET application using this control.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
Display Google Analytics Map in ASP.NET application using this control.

The control use Data Feed Request for Google Analytics Data Export API.
If number of markers too big, control on a page will loading very long.




(images shown statistics for different site)

The first version was created by Brian P. Hamachek, second by Ilya P. Klementiev.

Library .net 2.0, c#, Visual Studio 2010
